MacCoffee led their team in appreciating security guards at G4S Security headquarters Nairobi on Friday, June 12. The colourful event saw some 30 security guards awarded with an array of MacCoffee products. The aim of the event was to celebrate and appreciate the guards as they continue to provide security in Kenya and around the world amidst the Covid-19 pandemic. Speaking at the event, regional head Abhishek Rana said, “MacCoffee appreciates the G4S security workforce and we are humbled by your dedication, commitment and efforts to continue providing security solutions despite the uncertain times the world is going through.” G4S Secure Solutions director Geoffrey Mwove also said they are grateful to the MacCoffee team coming to celebrate some of the decorated officers who have been standing in the frontline during the pandemic. Edited by EKibii